{"tid":871993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新任台灣駐港代表仍未獲發簽證　陸委會：須看港府意願","createTime":"2018-10-22T11:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T12:11:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e373eb31696bc4bfdfac60a428432daaa0e88414","tid":871993,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181022/s00004/0c54b32d070c385006faa747dedd36ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181022%2Fs00004%2F0c54b32d070c385006faa747dedd36ba.jpg&h=d21ae21a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣大陸委員會6月中旬宣布，由盧長水出任香港辦事處長一職，惟4個月過去，本港入境處至今仍未核發工作簽證。陸委會主委陳明通今日前往立法院接受質詢時，稱陸委會已與港府「積極交涉」，惟須看對方意願。<br />\n<br />\n陳明通指，現時陸委會仍正了解不發簽證原因，並與港府「積極交涉」，惟仍要看對方的意願看。他又舉例，指過去雖然試過13個月不發簽證的紀錄，但他們不希望如此情況再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n入境處早前拒絕《金融時報》亞洲新聞主編、香港外國記者會（FCC）第一副主席馬凱（Victor Mallet）工作簽證續簽申請，引起輿論爭議。<br />\n<br />\n（中央社）"},{"pid":"2281591a0352aee7e0aaadda99c9486118925f7a","tid":871993,"uid":38194,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"臭支那成日做埋啲小動作，真係開波又唔夠膽"},{"pid":"7a08a9ccc939bc200e0451acc55f9182e3521e1f","tid":871993,"uid":200936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"弱撚智"},{"pid":"5519fae109511aed08fdce837146e9268d588098","tid":871993,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2281591a0352aee7e0aaadda99c9486118925f7a","tid":871993,"uid":38194,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"臭支那成日做埋啲小動作，真係開波又唔夠膽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"港共殖民政府依家係衝出去, 擋係支那面前食子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb70d437cc999faa9e8e97dff102acd020e5bc2","tid":871993,"uid":82640,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2281591a0352aee7e0aaadda99c9486118925f7a","tid":871993,"uid":38194,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"臭支那成日做埋啲小動作，真係開波又唔夠膽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"遲早台灣反擊中共港共先柒<br />\n台灣自從退出聯合國後無咩名譽可以爭行務實路線<br />\n根本唔care對岸啲神功戲<br />\n問題係台灣要落中共港共面好易<br />\n<br />\n例如打出入境印上中國護照、特區護照上面<br />\n中共唔通打印上台灣度報復咩<br />\n台灣仲開心啦<br />\n<br />\n大陸太為面<br />\n乜都要形式主義行先<br />\n搞到台灣仲有大把野撚大陸"},{"pid":"3df6edbd8b762b249549086e0887448d9d01a435","tid":871993,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"搞鳩特衰護照入台證就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d08d634347ae649e101de1bf5f22200f7fa8879","tid":871993,"uid":52943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:05:26.000Z","msg":"即時唔簽入台證比港豬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba58f5dab7839ca278dc4487e6f8a4ea97b94fb","tid":871993,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:07:04.000Z","msg":"照辦煮碗取消港駐台人員簽證"},{"pid":"fefc246868fea4452a25dc7566ef3d77886e9c89","tid":871993,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"香港人咁鍾意去台灣<br />\n咪搞搞振啦"}]}